不要欺负大杨哥、小杨哥，你直播的时候给你捧场。什么玩意儿，我有太多手段知道你干什么。太欺负人，咱真不闹事，各做各的平台生意，不能这样搞，为了做生意，没有底线去搞流量。」 此外，辛巴在提到卢文庆时还表示「你刚刚在东莞被判了，判三缓四还是判三缓一，具体什么原因，好像也和做电商有关系，弄虚作假吧，你是三只羊的合伙人是吧，监外执行是吧。」辛巴小杨哥风波升级：辛巴爆料三只羊女主播沫沫被抓，曾志伟连夜改名 _ 腾讯新闻三只羊女主播沫沫已有 9 个月未更新"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "9 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/666157875"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IvbLopMjmyKBXEAMaCTExMDMxMzAzNyDz4t62BjAAODBAHXIJNjY2MTU3ODc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}}